This repository contains the code for a functional and user-friendly stopwatch web application.
Designed for accuracy and ease of use, the stopwatch allows users to measure elapsed time with precision.

Features
Start, reset and lap: Basic controls for managing the stopwatch.
Lap Time Recording: Option to record lap times during the stopwatch session.
Digital Display: Clear and precise time display in hours, minutes, seconds, and milliseconds.
Responsive Design: Optimized for both desktop and mobile devices.
User-Friendly Interface: Simple and intuitive controls for a seamless user experience.
Technologies Used are:
HTML for the basic structure
CSS for styling and layout
JavaScript for stopwatch functionality and time management
Installation
Clone this repository: git clone https://github.com/sreejanellurii/stopwatch.git
Navigate to the project directory: cd stopwatch
Open index.html in your web browser to use the stopwatch.
Contributing:
Contributions to enhance the functionality or design of the stopwatch are welcome. Please feel free to open issues or submit pull requests.



